It will happen, when they ask you, ‘Where shall we go out?’ then you shall tell them, ‘Yahweh says: 
“Such as are for death, to death; 
such as are for the sword, to the sword; 
such as are for the famine, to the famine; 
and such as are for captivity, to captivity.” ’

I will make them to pass with your enemies into a land which you don’t know; 
for a fire is kindled in my anger, 
which will burn on you.”
